    {
      "id": "PopularPost101678",
      "post_content": "@brothersbutler:  \n  \nYour opponent's [Leyline of Sanctity](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Leyline of Sanctity) forbids you to even target him. This means that you can't even cast a [Fireball](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Fireball) with that player among its targets. So [Leyline of Punishment](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Leyline of Punishment) does nothing in this case. **But**, it does make non-targeted spells' damage unpreventable (for example, you can cast a [Volcanic Fallout](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Volcanic Fallout) and it will deal damage and kill creatures with toughness up to 2, even if they have protection from it)",
      "posted_by": "Falgorn",
      "html": "<div class=\"post oddItem\" id=\"PopularPost101678\">\n<span id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl01_post\">@brothersbutler:<br/><br/>Your opponent's <a class=\"autoCard\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Leyline of Sanctity\">Leyline of Sanctity</a> forbids you to even target him. This means that you can't even cast a <a class=\"autoCard\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Fireball\">Fireball</a> with that player among its targets. So <a class=\"autoCard\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Leyline of Punishment\">Leyline of Punishment</a> does nothing in this case. <b>But</b>, it does make non-targeted spells' damage unpreventable (for example, you can cast a <a class=\"autoCard\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Volcanic Fallout\">Volcanic Fallout</a> and it will deal damage and kill creatures with toughness up to 2, even if they have protection from it)</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl01_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl01_reportAbuseLink\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy2685\">Falgorn</span>\r\n                                (9/12/2010 3:52:47 PM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainConten